proof: let [T0, T1] (s0: (T0 -> T1) -> T1, s1: (T0 -> T1, T1) -> T0) satisfy { forall(x0: T0 -> T1, x1: T0) { not is_constant[T0, T1](x0) or s0(x0) = x0(x1) } and forall(x2: T0 -> T1, x3: T1) { x2(s1(x2, x3)) != x3 or is_constant[T0, T1](x2) } }
function[T0, T1](x0: T0 -> T1, x1: T1) { x0(s1(x0, x1)) != x1 or is_constant[T0, T1](x0) }[T, U](constant[T, U](u), u)
function[T0, T1](x0: T1, x1: T0) { constant[T0, T1](x0, x1) = x0 }[T, U](u, s1(constant[T, U](u), u))
function(x0: U) { constant[T, U](u, s1(constant[T, U](u), x0)) != x0 }(u)
